s known for its ownership stakes in arlington park and churchill downs race tracks as well as for rail car and defense manufacturing contents  early life and education  military career  family  career  awards and honors  see also  references  external links early life and educationedit duchossois graduated from morgan park military academy and attended washington and lee university before starting active military service during world war ii military careeredit he served in five european campaigns including normandy where he was a commander with the th tank destroyer battalion he served as the military governor for the region of eichstätt and attained the rank of major before he was released from active service in  he received a purple heart for his injuries in combat at the moselle river familyedit he married his high school sweetheart beverly thrall his son craig j duchossois is chief executive officer of the duchossois group inc and serves as chairman of the board of visitors of the united states naval academy careeredit richard duchossois joined thrall car manufacturing company after world war ii and became ceo in  in  the firm purchased chamberlain manufacturing corp with duchossois becoming its chairman at the same time he retained the chairmanship of the parent company but appointed his son as ceo in  as chairman of renamed duchossois industries dii he purchased arlington park race track in  arlington park merged with churchill downs incorporated where dii has several seats on the board of directors he also owned des moines tv station kdsmtv formerly kcbrtv from  to  he serves as a director of tcmc inc the emirates world series of racing and the thoroughbred racing association awards and honorsedit he received a purple heart and two bronze stars for his military service in world war ii his awards include the  american jockey clubs gold medal the  special sovereign award from the jockey club of canada and lord derby award from the horserace writers and reporters association of great britain the joe palmer award for meritorious service to racing from the national turf writers association the  eclipse award of merit and selection to the chicagoland sports hall of fame he received an honorary doctor of laws degree from washington and lee in  washington and lee university honored him with the washington award with his wife judi in  they received the sword of loyola award from loyola university chicago for their philanthropy see alsoedit arlington classic beverly d stakes eclipse special award pucker up stakes sussex stakes referencesedit  richard l duchossois businessweekcom   a b man behind the million   a b c world war ii duchossois richard   a b c arlington owner duchossois at  fights cancer and for his track httpwwwdailyheraldcomarticlenews   years after arlington park fire richard duchossois is still at the track httpwwwchicagobusinesscomarticleissueyearsafterarlingtonparkfirerichardduchossoisisstillatthetrack  a b c washington and lee honors richard l duchossois with washington award wluedu   dick duchossois returns to normandy to honor ddays th anniversary dnainfo chicago   loyola to honor dick and judi duchossois and mike my lehoang md nov  at stritch annual awards dinner newswisecom  duchossois industries website los angeles times article august   ntra eclipse award external linksedit usma west point oral history interview of richard duchossois httpwwwwestpointcohorginterviewsseekstrikedestroyatankdestroyercommanderrollsacrosseurope national world war ii museum oral history interview of richard duchossois httpwwwwwonlineorgtermspage retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlerichardlduchossoisoldid categories american business executivesamerican sports businesspeopleliving peoplemorgan park academy alumniwashington and lee university alumniamerican military personnel of world war iipeople from barrington illinoisamerican horse racing industry executivesamerican racehorse owners and breederschurchill downs execut