d going forward well look at a broader range of investments mr flannery said we dont need to necessarily own  percent of the assetthe enterprise provides a new executive perch for mr flannery  who has worked for the family for about  years most recently as executive vice president and chief financial officer at duchossois group since to this point the investment arms and four major companies owned by the family have all been run through elmhurstbased duchossois group inc which is also the largest owner of the horse racetrack company churchill downs inc the management team for that company includes richard as chairman his son as ceo and robert fealy as president and chief operating officer the biggest of duchossois groups wholly owned companies is garage door opener company chamberlain group inc also based in elmhurst the company has holdings valued at more than  billion with about  employees in north america europe and asia according to the companys website duchossois industries inc craig j duchossois richard l duchossois consumer products real estate technology transportation private equity todays crains get our daily roundup of important business news read next this lincolnshire mortgage giant called it quits heres why morningstar buys stake in responsible investing firm big state pension takes a hatchet to hedge funds william blair exits muni bond business the duchossois group